'''Dreel'starn''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. It was located to the southwestern part of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent. To the north-northwest was the city of [[Urval'starn]].

